            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The "experts" tell you to risk your money in the market to get growth.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Then, they tell you to move to "safe" bonds as you get older, where your money is eaten alive by inflation.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 font-bold leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This is the <strong>Retiree's Dilemma:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-4 mb-6">
                <li class="text-xl leading-relaxed flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-myBlue font-bold mr-3">&#9656;</span>
