                </li>
                <li class="text-xl leading-relaxed flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-myBlue font-bold mr-3">&#9656;</span>
                    <strong>OPTION B (INFLATION):</strong> Flee to "safety" and watch your purchasing power die a slow death.
                </li>
            </ul>

